 kako teku godine,

742
00:52:18,220 --> 00:52:19,660
 i mi se jako puno

743
00:52:19,660 --> 00:52:20,700
 i racionaliziramo

744
00:52:20,700 --> 00:52:22,880
 i dođeš u nekakav materializam,

745
00:52:22,880 --> 00:52:24,460
 i onda to sjećanje

746
00:52:24,460 --> 00:52:25,400
 na Boga bljedi,

747
00:52:25,400 --> 00:52:27,320
 ako nije zaliveno vjerom,

748
00:52:27,320 --> 00:52:28,960
 ako nije zaliveno vjerom

749
00:52:28,960 --> 00:52:29,540
 u obitelji,

750
00:52:29,540 --> 00:52:30,880
 s roditeljima i tako to.

