838
00:55:23,440 --> 00:55:25,340
 jedne zajednice?

839
00:55:25,340 --> 00:55:28,740
 Da, puno ih je.

840
00:55:29,120 --> 00:55:31,540
 Mislim, to je ipak ono, institucija

841
00:55:31,540 --> 00:55:33,600
 sačinjena od ljudi koji, ok, jasno

842
00:55:33,600 --> 00:55:35,740
 trude se činiti dobro, ali

843
00:55:35,740 --> 00:55:36,980
 koje su zamke

844
