847
00:55:43,280 --> 00:55:43,860
 na greškama.

848
00:55:43,860 --> 00:55:45,420
 To je ko obitelj.

849
00:55:45,420 --> 00:55:47,440
 Ko obitelj.

850
00:55:47,440 --> 00:55:49,180
 Ne kažem da je obitelj, kažem

851
00:55:49,180 --> 00:55:49,960
 ko obitelj.

852
00:55:49,960 --> 00:55:50,840
 jer ovisi.

853
00:55:50,840 --> 00:55:52,160
 Postoji

854
00:55:52,160 --> 00:55:55,600
