862
00:56:06,200 --> 00:56:06,740
 zajednica.

863
00:56:06,740 --> 00:56:07,820
 Ali

864
00:56:07,820 --> 00:56:10,220
 zajednica je

865
00:56:10,220 --> 00:56:10,740
