945
00:58:43,140 --> 00:58:45,220
 to jedno Bog može

946
00:58:45,220 --> 00:58:47,360
 složiti da tako funkcionira

947
00:58:47,360 --> 00:58:48,200
 18 godina.

948
00:58:48,200 --> 00:58:50,280
 Božja milost, ništa drugo.

949
00:58:50,280 --> 00:58:51,900
 Da smo mi to po nekoj svoje pameti.

950
00:58:51,900 --> 00:58:52,580
 Ma kako.

951
00:58:52,580 --> 00:58:55,120
 Zašto?

952
00:58:55,120 --> 00:58:57,100
 Jer zajednica traži

953
00:58:57,100 --> 00:59:00,520
 da s nekim se češeš

954
00:59:00,520 --> 00:59:01,720
 non stop ramena.

955
00:59:02,100 --> 00:59:02,660
 non stop.

956
00:59:02,660 --> 00:59:04,440
 Sve je tako

957
00:59:04,440 --> 00:59:06,560
 blisko.

958
00:59:06,560 --> 00:59:07,800
 U smislu,

959
00:59:07,800 --> 00:59:08,860
 non stop si s ljudima

960
00:59:08,860 --> 00:59:09,960
 i non stop si u odnosu

961
00:59:09,960 --> 00:59:11,100
 i non stop si u duhovnim

962
00:59:11,100 --> 00:59:12,540
 nekim isto i stvarnostima.

963
00:59:12,540 --> 00:59:12,860
 Znači,

964
00:59:12,860 --> 00:59:13,720
 molimš za nekoga

965
00:59:13,720 --> 00:59:15,340
 i svi imamo svoje vizije,

966
00:59:15,340 --> 00:59:16,800
 svi imamo percepciju

967
00:59:16,800 --> 00:59:17,880
 šta bi zajednica trebala,

968
00:59:17,880 --> 00:59:18,880
 šta bi ti trebao raditi,

969
00:59:18,880 --> 00:59:19,860
 šta bi ja trebao raditi.

970
00:59:20,680 --> 00:59:24,480
 i to sve dođe u jedno ono baš trenje

971
00:59:24,480 --> 00:59:27,040
 koje gdje ti zapravo si prisiljen

972
00:59:27,040 --> 00:59:29,000
