1512
01:25:10,620 --> 01:25:12,260
 To im je bilo potrebno za ovaj projekt.

1513
01:25:12,260 --> 01:25:15,660
 I Marko je, on i suproga i djeca,

1514
01:25:15,660 --> 01:25:18,680
